			<div id="content-rag_head">
				<div id="headerrag">RELATIONAL AGENTS GROUP</div>
				Relational Agents are computer agents designed to form long-term, social-emotional relationships with their users.
				We are investigating the use of these agents in task domains in which human-agent relationships actually improve task outcomes, such as in coaching, counseling, psychotherapy and healthcare. 
			</div>
</td></tr></table>

